{"tid":784393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【可直接飲用】【新技術在沙漠「空氣中抽水」】","createTime":"2018-08-18T10:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T13:56:22.000Z","uid":86509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e18d0630e593d4cd36c209fd93ce8612ff8dde0","tid":784393,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/933678963490839/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F933678963490839%2F&d=A9Pa8XVvC8k8JunG8EBBMGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4d2eb1ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/933678963490839/</a><br />\n<br />\n【可直接飲用】<br />\n【新技術在沙漠「空氣中抽水」】<br />\n<br />\n美國有科學家早前研發出一項技術，就算在沙漠地區，都能直接在空氣中收集水份。<br />\n<br />\n這種複合晶體稱為「金屬有機框架」，利用有內外兩個箱的裝置，在入面的箱上，放置有機晶體。<br />\n<br />\n在濕度高的晚上，晶體與空氣接觸後就會吸收水份，並在白天時將晶體內的水份蒸發，再排到外面的箱凝結，最終流到箱底，將水收集就能直接飲用。<br />\n<br />\n團隊實地試驗並作改良，乾旱地區的民眾有望受惠。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#金屬有機框架　#複合晶體　#沙漠　#水份　#新聞通識"},{"pid":"2c398251a65d2c9e805efe60d286004c3b4ff148","tid":784393,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"咁咪有機會綠化沙漠囉"},{"pid":"f591c75dd6f3b615a950135fd5ea144af7e49c0a","tid":784393,"uid":49392,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"我屋企都有部，叫抽濕機"},{"pid":"411d537eb17b530c9b51c290b6dc94366dec63ed","tid":784393,"uid":51720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都有部，叫抽濕機</blockquote><br />\n仲有光明頂果位 :o<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"1c37952fc163fb6c6feb780e4222f590fa08fcf9","tid":784393,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f591c75dd6f3b615a950135fd5ea144af7e49c0a","tid":784393,"uid":49392,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"我屋企都有部，叫抽濕機"},"citedBy":1,